# Thai tickers (SET)

## Storage / Yahoo
- SET symbols stored/displayed with `-BK` suffix (e.g. `TISCO-BK`)
- `storageTicker()` / `toYahooTicker()` handle normalization — do not strip suffix blindly

## Transaction form
- Typing plain `TISCO` should preview `TISCO-BK`; changing ticker must not reset market from SET → US
- Currency follows market: SET → THB; allow THB on other markets when user selects it
- Persist `currency` on transaction rows; dividends default check `currency` field

## Holdings metadata
- `currency: THB`, `market: SET` for Thai holdings
- Migrations `011`, `012` backfilled stale USD-on-Thai rows — new code should infer, not rely on DB alone
